  "response": "For rooted Android phones, some effective apps for tracking a lost or stolen device include:\n\n1. Prey Anti-Theft\n- Works on rooted devices\n- Tracks location\n- Remote lock and wipe capabilities\n- Cross-platform support\n\n2. Find My Device (Google)\n- Built-in Android feature\n- Can track even after factory reset if Find My Device is enabled\n- Works with Google account\n\n3. Cerberus\n- Advanced tracking features\n- Works on rooted devices\n- Can survive factory reset\n- Remote control options\n\n4. ESET Mobile Security\n- Good for rooted phones\n- Tracking and anti-theft features\n- Real-time location tracking\n\n5. Lookout Security\n- Rooted device support\n- Location tracking\n- Remote lock and wipe\n\nThese apps offer various features like GPS tracking, remote locking, data wiping, and sometimes even taking photos of the person using the device. Choose based on your specific needs and preferences. Remember to set up the tracking app and enable its features before losing your phone.",
